<plot>A mockumentary in the tradition of Waiting for Guffman, the Four Questions blurs the lines between fiction and reality as the cast goes into the streets of New York City and interacts with unsuspecting people. The Four Questions follows a New York City street performance group who sing doo-wop versions of modern dance songs on the streets and in the subways of New York.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?558992</url></doc>
